messages.content: I'm working under the famous immunologist, Dr. Anthony S. Fauci, as his assistant. He will be addressing HIV/AIDS patients tomorrow and has asked me to send him all his HIV-related papers. I want you to look for Dr. Anthony S. Fauci's papers related to HIV/AIDS and provide me with the links.

reasoning: To find Dr. Anthony S. Fauci's HIV/AIDS papers with links, I will first search Google Scholar using his name as author and 'HIV' as keywords. This will likely yield a comprehensive list of his relevant research articles and their links.

messages.name: google_scholar

reasoning: I have retrieved a list of Dr. Anthony S. Fauci's HIV/AIDS papers with links from Google Scholar. I will now provide the user with the titles and links to these publications as requested.

messages.content:
Here are Dr. Anthony S. Fauci's key HIV/AIDS-related papers with their respective links:

1. Immunopathogenic mechanisms of HIV infection – https://www.acpjournals.org/doi/abs/10.7326/0003-4819-124-7-199604010-00006
2. Ending the HIV/AIDS pandemic – https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC5823353/
3. Ending the HIV epidemic: a plan for the United States – https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jama/article-abstract/2724455
4. Thirty years of HIV and AIDS: future challenges and opportunities – https://www.acpjournals.org/doi/abs/10.7326/0003-4819-154-11-201106070-00345
5. The AIDS epidemic—considerations for the 21st century – https://www.nejm.org/doi/abs/10.1056/NEJM199909303411406
6. An HIV vaccine is essential for ending the HIV/AIDS pandemic – https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jama/article-abstract/2656461
7. Toward an AIDS-free generation – https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jama/article-abstract/1221711
8. Twenty-five years of HIV/AIDS – https://www.science.org/doi/abs/10.1126/science.1131993
9. The human immunodeficiency virus: infectivity and mechanisms of pathogenesis – https://www.science.org/doi/abs/10.1126/science.3277274
10. Immunopathogenic mechanisms in human immunodeficiency virus (HIV) infection – https://www.acpjournals.org/doi/abs/10.7326/0003-4819-114-8-678

If you need more papers or a complete list beyond these top results, please let me know!

Dr. Anthony S. Fauci will explain HIV Vaccines to the audience. He will discuss how hiv vaccines are designed to teach the immune system to fight and recognize HIV, and also how to control HIV in patients. I was asked to look for the latest news related to HIV/AIDS vaccines. 

I want you to look for news that was released in the year 2025 that is related to HIV/AIDS vaccines.

reasoning: To find the latest news specifically related to HIV/AIDS vaccines released in 2025, I will perform a Google News search filtered for this topic and year.

reasoning: I have found a wide variety of engaging HIV/AIDS posters and images suitable for conference use, including sources for free downloads, educational awareness, and design templates. I will now provide a concise list of key poster links and resources for easy access and printing.

messages.content:
Here are engaging HIV/AIDS poster and image resources suitable for your conference:

1. Venngage – Educational HIV/AIDS Poster: https://venngage.com/templates/posters/educational-facts-and-information-hiv-aids-poster-e204a0c6-dae8-47a0-9725-cc0ef1f0c37a
2. National Library of Medicine – International AIDS Poster Collection: https://www.nlm.nih.gov/exhibition/aids-posters/index.html
3. iStock – AIDS Poster Stock Art (royalty-free, some licensable): https://www.istockphoto.com/photos/aids-poster
4. Canva – Free Printable HIV/AIDS Poster Templates: https://www.canva.com/posters/templates/hiv-aids/
5. ShareAmerica – Free Awareness Poster: https://archive-share.america.gov/raise-hiv-aids-awareness-with-this-free-poster/index.html
6. Vecteezy – HIV/AIDS Transmission Poster Infographics: https://www.vecteezy.com/vector-art/13373906-hiv-and-aids-transmission-ways-poster-with-info-vector
7. Memorial Art Gallery (U. of Rochester) – Art, Activism & AIDS Posters: https://mag.rochester.edu/exhibitions/up-against-the-wall/
8. UNAIDS – World AIDS Day Poster Materials: https://www.unaids.org/en/resources/campaigns/WAD2016/materials
9. PosterMyWall – Editable HIV/AIDS Awareness Poster: https://www.postermywall.com/index.php/art/template/67bd5cb7a271b96cfc31520ec717a13c/hiv-aids-awareness-poster-design-template

These sites offer a range of modern, informative, and visually striking posters—many are free to use or edit. For more options or printable, customizable templates, see also Canva and PosterMyWall. If you need printable high-resolution or specific theme suggestions, let me know!
